# [color=hotpink] What is True Love? [/color]:heart: 
True Love is something indescribable.... Just kidding, it&#39;s a forum mafia setup! 
All players have no abilities, however all players are lovers with another player! 
If your lover ever dies, you die! You share a night chat with your lover. 
However, don&#39;t be deceived! Your lover isn&#39;t necessarily the same alignment as you! 
Both mafia are lovers with a member of the town! 

#  [color=hotpink] Gameplay [/color] :video_game: 
The game is nightless. 
Lynch is majority based. 
When the number of mafia = the number of remaining town, mafia win.
The mafia share a day chat.
All lovers share a day chat.

#  [color=hotpink] Rolecards [/color] :flower_playing_cards: 
&gt; # [color=green]Town Lover[/color]
&gt; You are a member of the town. You are in love with (PlayerName). If they ever die, you will also die.
*Your goal is to see all of the mafia dead.*

&gt; #  [color=red]Mafia Lover[/color] 
&gt; You are a member of the mafia! You are in love with (PlayerName). If they ever die, you will also die. Your fellow mafia member is (PlayerName.)
*Your goal is to outnumber the members of the town.* 

#  [color=hotpink] Rolelist[/color] :scroll: 
[color=red]**2x Mafia Lovers**[/color]
 [color=green]**6x Town Lovers**[/color]

